# WATI API REFERENCE

This is the curated Wati API specification covering the endpoints
used by Fabric. Use these endpoint definitions as the authoritative
source for paths, methods, request bodies, and response shapes.

Rules:
- If a feature uses an endpoint defined here, use the exact field
  names and types from this spec.
- If a feature requires data NOT covered here, mark relevant fields
  as ⚠ GAP. Do NOT invent endpoints, paths, or field shapes.
- This spec is the authoritative reference. Do not assume Wati has
  endpoints beyond what is listed here.

